text: Misaki Noro (born 12 April 1996) is a Japanese female water polo player who participated at the 2017 World Aquatic Championships and 2019 World Aquatic Championships. == References == == Other websites == * misaki-noro swimswam * Asian+Games+Day+2 Noro+Misaki zimbio Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese water polo players
